      "summary": "<p>Charles Azar, pastry in its many forms</p>",
      "introduction": "<p>Charles Azar has long been interested in pastry in all its many forms. Beyond mastering the essential techniques, he has developed his own unique touch and style. For several years now, he has been running a pastry consulting firm, working on local and international projects, and has opened his second artisanal ice cream shop, « Le Flocon, » where he works exclusively with pure, natural, seasonal ingredients. »</p>",
